<plot>Margarita is a tough woman who, at a young age, experienced several difficulties in life. She was just a little girl when her father left her mother for another woman. As the eldest in the family, Margarita shouldered the responsibility of being the breadwinner. She only has her childhood friend Rodrigo by her side as she struggles through life's difficulties. Along the way, Margarita will meet Bernard, a rich and influential man who will eventually fall in love with her. Margarita will later find herself torn not only between these two men, but also between her dream of happiness and her desire of revenge.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?357703</url></doc>
